          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "Four silicon detectors were used to detect protons",
                " (sensitive area was from 2 to 3 mm). These detectors",
                "were placed in one plane - horizontal or other.",
                "Detectors were fixed on a table in the scattering",
                "chamber with a diameter 23 cm at different angles",
                "relative to the deuteron beam at a distance of 75 mm",
                "from the target. At the table rotation an angle of",
                "proton detection remained unchanged. One detector was",
                "used to measure the angle and energy dependences.",
                "This detector was placed on an annular platform",
                "outside the scattering chamber."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Finely divided boron powder enriched in 10B isotope to",
                "85% and deposited on a thin gold backing (0.22 mg/cm2)",
                "was used as a target. Target thickness was evaluated",
                "by weighing and was 1.0+ -0.1 mg/cm2."
              ]
